Package: this.path
Version: 1.2.0
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Title: Get Executing Script's Path, from 'Rgui', 'RStudio', 'VSCode',
    'source()', and 'Rscript' (Shells Including Windows Command Line /
    / Unix Terminal)
Description: Determine the path of the executing script. Works when
    running a line or selection in 'Rgui', 'RStudio', and 'VSCode',
    when using 'source()', 'sys.source()', 'debugSource()' in 'RStudio',
    'testthat::source_file()', and 'knitr::knit()', and when running
    from a shell.
Author: Andrew Simmons
Maintainer: Andrew Simmons <akwsimmo@gmail.com>
Suggests: utils, microbenchmark
Enhances: knitr, rprojroot, rstudioapi, testthat
URL: https://github.com/ArcadeAntics/this.path
BugReports: https://github.com/ArcadeAntics/this.path/issues
Biarch: TRUE
Encoding: UTF-8
